Quickstrike:




Quickstrike looked around. Most of the Maximals retreated. It was 
almost over. He wanted to make it clear that Predacons would never 
back down now. He spotted Deemos and Atma. He slowly approached them. 
He had his head ducked and a glower on his face. He was ready to 
shoot them.
